def ATR(df, n):  
    i = 0  
    TR_l = [0]  
    while i < df.index[-1]:  
        TR = max(df.get_value(i + 1, 'high'), df.get_value(i, 'close')) - min(df.get_value(i + 1, 'low'), df.get_value(i, 'close'))  
        TR_l.append(TR)  
        i = i + 1  
    TR_s = pd.Series(TR_l)  
    ATR = pd.Series(pd.ewma(TR_s, span = n, min_periods = n), name = 'atr')  
    df = df.join(ATR)
    return df

def Open_S(NIFTY50, N50MINUTE, open_multiplier, close_multiplier):
    trade_long=1
    trade_short=1
    long_pos = 0
    short_pos = 0
    day_order=0
    total_pl=0
    N_days=len(NIFTY50)-1
    trade_dict = {}
    #open_multiplier=1.05
    #close_multiplier=2.5
    for X in NIFTY50.index:
        #if X < N_days and (NIFTY50.at[X,'date']+BDay()).strftime('%a')=="Fri":
        if X < N_days:
            # previous day stretch
            stretch_10sma=NIFTY50.at[X,'stretch_10sma']
            # NIFTY open
            n50open=NIFTY50.at[X,'open']
            # NIFTY high

            # NIFTY low
            n50low=NIFTY50.at[X,'low']
            # NIFTY close
            n50close=NIFTY50.at[X,'close']
            # run minute loop from tradeday (day+1)
            tradeday=NIFTY50.at[X+1,'date']
            # look for data between tradeday and tradeday+1 days
            dayafter=tradeday+BDay()
            #print tradeday, dayafter, stretch_10sma
            pl=0
            for ti,op,hi,lo,cl in N50MINUTE.query('date_time >= @tradeday and date_time <= @dayafter').itertuples(index=False):
                # if first bar
                # set entry,stop,profit target for the day based on first 1 min bar today
                # and previous days stretch_10sma
                if ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') == "09:16:00":
                #if tradeday.strftime('%a')=="Tue" or tradeday.strftime('%a')=="Thu":
                    longentry,longstop,longtarget = op+stretch_10sma*open_multiplier,op,op+stretch_10sma*close_multiplier
                    shortentry,shortstop,shorttarget = op-stretch_10sma*open_multiplier,op,op-stretch_10sma*close_multiplier
                if ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') != "09:16:00":
                    #limit number of order per day to 1

                    #if cl > longentry and trade_long == 1 and day_order != 1 and longstop < max(n50close,n50open):
                    if cl > longentry and trade_long == 1 and day_order != 1 :
                        # enter long

                        long_pos = 1
                        o_time=ti

                        o_price=longentry
                    if hi > longtarget and day_order ==1 and trade_long == 1 and long_pos == 1:

                        # enter short

    avg_loss=trade.query('win_loss == "Loss"')[['pl']].apply(lambda row: np.mean(row),axis=0).values[0]
    #return trade, win_pct,total_pl,total_trades,profit_factor,avg_win,avg_loss,open_multiplier,close_multiplier
    return win_pct,total_pl,total_trades,profit_factor,avg_win,avg_loss,open_multiplier,close_multiplier
